{"word":"G2425 - ἱκανός - hikanós - hik-an-os' - Able","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱκανός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hikanós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hik-an-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Able</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பாத்திரனான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"sufficient"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03BA;&#x03C9;</b> <b>hiko&#x0304;</b> (<b>&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> or <b>&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x03BA;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;</b>; akin to <a href=\"#/G2240 - ἥκω - hḗkō - hay'-ko/2240\">G2240</a>; to <i>arrive</i>); <i>competent</i> (as if <i>coming</i> in season), that is, <i>ample</i> (in amount) or <i>fit</i> (in character): - able, + content, enough, good, great, large, long (while), many, meet, much, security, sore, sufficient, worthy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2425/2425\">G2425</a>, <a href=\"#/G2426/2426\">G2426</a>, <a href=\"#/G2427/2427\">G2427</a>"}]}